page_observer_backend.description:
Choose how Bitfocus Companion Bridge should read live rendered state for this imported page. The default is taken from the main Companion device configuration. Network ports are configured once in the main setup and reused here.

**Surface mode — most secure default**
{surface_mode}

After the observer surface is created in Companion, set its Home Page / Current Page to the imported page. Also turn **Restrict pages accessible to this surface** ON and allow only that page.

