manage_sensors.description:
Manage imported entities for `{page_title}`. `No change` leaves an entity exactly as it is. `Disable entity` keeps the Home Assistant entity registry entry but stops the integration from loading the entity. `Delete permanently` removes the entity registry entry and removes it from this page import metadata. Use permanent delete carefully because dashboards and automations can reference the entity.

